---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="relative py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <SectionHeader eyebrow="About" title="Engineer. Builder. Leader." />
    <div class="reveal mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-4xl gap-8 text-lg text-mist-300 md:grid-cols-2">
      <p>
        I am an engineering leader and applied AI builder. Over the past decade I have shipped systems at scale across identity verification, ML-powered trust, and AI agent infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today I lead 19 engineers at Airbnb. My systems protect millions of users daily. I am channeling that work into AI-native products, voice-first interfaces, and technical ventures shipped under my own name.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
